Verbal morphology paradigms loosely based on 
Ventsislav Zhechev's BA Thesis:

 "A Finite-State Approach to the Inflectional Morphology of the Bulgarian Verb"

Special thanks to:

* Prof. George Mitrevski at Auburn University for providing his Macedonian Reverse Dictionary.
* Igor Kalkov for answering a lot of questions.
* Rosen Vladimirov for responding to questions.
